---
title: Harissa Sausage Naanizza with Roasted Pepper, Cheddar and Baby Gem Salad
description: This Harissa Sausage Naanizza is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
